6133, "likes": 62, "replies": 6, "retweets": 11, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062182320648450048", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2062182320648450423", "text": "US crude imports by origin incl w/w changes in bkpd\nCanada -152 to 3,677\nMexico +178 to 323\nSaudi Arabia +283 to 283\nVenezuela +154 to 568\nBrazil +214 to 414\nColombia -44 to 167\nIraq +43 to 43\nNigeria +23 to 23\nEcuador +186 to 300\nLibya +8 to 8\n\nEIA #oott", "time": "14:39", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 119642, "views": 7219, "likes": 35, "replies": 2, "retweets": 8, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062182949747864064", "url": "https://x.com/OilandEnergy/status/2062182949747864052", "text": "U.S. crude inventories fell by 8 million barrels last week, far exceeding expectations and pushing stockpiles 3% below the five-year average. The draw comes as oil demand remains strong and global supply risks persist. #Oil #EIA #OOTT #EnergyMarkets \n\nhttps://t.co/SaX1VOeT2K", "time": "14:41", "author": "OilandEnergy", "author_name": "OilPrice.com", "followers": 95942, "views": 7978, "likes": 89, "replies": 5, "retweets": 25, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062206115861996032", "url": "https://x.com/profutures2012/status/2062206115861995726", "text": "We have lost 2.5 days of cover in 2.5 months?\n\nI'll swallow my pride and admit...\n\nChina and US admin have played this masterfully so far\n\n#OOTT\n\nIts all band aids and duct tape and will end... but not just yet", "time": "16:13", "author": "profutures2012", "author_name": "Mark Johnston", "followers": 9859, "views": 16900, "likes": 57, "replies": 3, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 21, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062211355868836096", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2062211355868836050", "text": "Charts on US petroleum inventories in million barrels (EIA) #oott https://t.co/WUZVAhbtaJ", "time": "16:34", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 119641, "views": 17951, "likes": 109, "replies": 4, "retweets": 30, "quotes": 6, "bookmarks": 18, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062212482140147968", "url": "https://x.com/PetroleumEcon/status/2062212482140147849", "text": "#Oil is facing a 'Great Inventory Drain' that is dragging inventories down at a pace without precedent and heading for the operational bottom of the barrel—with severe consequences #OOTT #energy\nhttps://t.co/NsDkQRmspy https://t.co/tlg00sEGKA", "time": "16:39", "author": "PetroleumEcon", "author_name": "Petroleum Economist", "followers": 67040, "views": 6549, "likes": 19, "replies": 3, "retweets": 9, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062218009276515072", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2062218009276514554", "text": "US implied oil demand (product supplied) in mbpd \nEIA\n#oott https://t.co/5Zrsqa7lkO", "time": "17:01", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 119641, "views": 5183, "likes": 27, "replies": 2, "retweets": 6, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062219083655898112", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2062219083655897481", "text": "US crude and refined product exports in mbpd (EIA) #oott https://t.co/39t9jjfAPg", "time": "17:05", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 119641, "views": 3711, "likes": 15, "replies": 0, "retweets": 4, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062221535411085056", "url": "https://x.com/OilandEnergy/status/2062221535411085428", "text": "Markets may be underestimating the post-Hormuz recovery timeline. Kuwait Petroleum says crude production would take up to 12 weeks to fully recover after a reopening, highlighting the risk of prolonged supply tightness. #CrudeOil #OOTT #EnergyMarkets \n\nhttps://t.co/zBW6LRWZGA", "time": "17:15", "author": "OilandEnergy", "author_name": "OilPrice.com", "followers": 95942, "views": 4429, "likes": 49, "replies": 5, "retweets": 17, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062242851149529088", "url": "https://x.com/BokehResearch/status/2062242851149529438", "text": "Kuwait says they can reach 70% oil capacity in ~7 weeks, and the remaining 30% in ~30 days.  That would mean net ~36 days of lost production after the SoH is open.  \n\nExtrapolate to 13.5mbpd of shut-ins across the gulf, it's 484mb of lost production after the SoH opens.\n\n#oott https://t.co/fgjPBR7sw", "time": "18:39", "author": "BokehResearch", "author_name": "BokehResearch", "followers": 346, "views": 22960, "likes": 33, "replies": 3, "retweets": 6, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 7, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062246448100471040", "url": "https://x.com/Riccardino999/status/2062246448100470794", "text": "#aet #afentra #oott\n\nWOW!\nWasn't expecting this placing!\n\n40m$ , 67p no warrants \n\nI can only think that together with 125m£ debt facility this means an acquisition is near \n\nI d say block 2/05 from Etu (needs money)\nOr block 0 from $cvx in partnership with others (mature but https://t.co/GlB5uuTKcT", "time": "18:54", "author": "Riccardino999", "author_name": "Mr Rhino", "followers": 1440, "views": 2295, "likes": 14, "replies": 4, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062275783926670080", "url": "https://x.com/OilandEnergy/status/2062275783926669595", "text": "At the start of 2026, markets feared an oil glut. Six months later, inventories are falling and supply security is a growing concern. The lesson: production capacity means little if barrels can’t reach consumers during a crisis. #OilMarkets #EnergySecurity #OOTT \n\nhttps://t.co/uFk5Oqd6Rd", "time": "20:50", "author": "OilandEnergy", "author_name": "OilPrice.com", "followers": 95942, "views": 2743, "likes": 30, "replies": 2, "retweets": 8, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062287989221338880", "url": "https://x.com/ZmansEnrgyBrain/status/2062287989221339407", "text": "Marco Rubio testified that large portions of the Strait of Hormuz had been mined by Iran ~ June 2, 2026, Senate Foreign Relations Committee. #OOTT", "time": "21:39", "author": "ZmansEnrgyBrain", "author_name": "Z4 Energy Research", "followers": 11776, "views": 5014, "likes": 21, "replies": 4, "retweets": 4, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062298614211194880", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2062298614211194998", "text": "WTI comparative inventory decreased 7.5 mmb to 29 mmb less than the 5-year average\nfor week ending May 29\n\nWTI price includes a $12 risk premium: \n\ninventories say $81, markets say $93\n#energy #OOTT #oilandgas #WTI #CrudeOil #fintwit #OPEC #Commodities #commoditiesmarket https://t.co/m9WFqJv81Q", "time": "22:21", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 52885, "views": 2607, "likes": 42, "replies": 4, "retweets": 12, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062310938338877952", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2062310938338877776", "text": "The US blockade is \"choking off\" Iran's production?@WoodMackenzie \n\nIran's \"choked off production\" still makes it the 9th largest oil producer in the world.\n\nTry objective reporting.\n\n#energy #OOTT #oilandgas #WTI #CrudeOil #fintwit #OPEC #Commodities #commoditiesmarket https://t.co/teyRdbhUr7", "time": "23:10", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 52885, "views": 3963, "likes": 36, "replies": 0, "retweets": 8, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 6, "labels": null}], "top_authors_by_tweets": [{"username": "staunovo", "name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 119643, "tweets": 36, "views": 132732, "likes": 629}, {"username": "ZmansEnrgyBrain", "name": "Z4 Energy Research", "followers": 11776, "tweets": 18, "views": 36912, "likes": 180}, {"username": "Rigzone", "name": "Rigzone", "followers": 108802, "tweets": 4, "views": 2475, "likes": 8}, {"username": "OilandEnergy", "name": "OilPrice.com", "followers": 95942, 